raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Babe!
Mabel: Are you ready yet!?
Player: For what?
Mabel: The party!!
Player: The party isn't for another few hours though
Mabel: But aren't we supposed to be there like super duper early just in case?
Player: Uhh I don't think so 😆
Mabel: Oh okay then 🥹
Player: Let me guess, you're nervous? 😁
Mabel: No way!!
Mabel: I'm totally a party animal!
Player: Riiight
Mabel: img: mabel/163
Mabel: I went to a party before, remember?!
Mabel: I'm THE party princess hehe
Player: I guess that's half true 😁
if Story.has_flag(\"NTSKiss\"):
	Mabel: Seems like things are going so fast these days
	Player: What do you mean?
	Mabel: Well we just.. y'know
	Mabel: Had our first kiss yesterday and today I might..
	Mabel: Thought: Is it really normal for girls to try kissing different guys?
	Mabel: Nevermind, I shouldn't think about this omg
	- Still on your mind?
		Player: Still on your mind?
		Mabel: Duh 🥰
		Mabel: Maybe I was no good at it but hopefully we can practice more 😚
		Player: Practice makes perfect 😘
	- Who knows. You might enjoy your next kiss more 👀
		Player: Who knows. You might enjoy your next kiss more 👀
		Mabel: I might totally chicken out 🐔🙈
else:
	Player: You'll have no problem with any of the party games then?
	Mabel: OMGG
	Mabel: I yield!!
	Mabel: Please don't remind me of that 😭
	Player: My bad mabes 😆
Mabel: Naomi just had to add something like that didn't she 🫠
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
	Mabel: Thought: I won't lose to Naomi though
	Mabel: Thought: I want to do what makes babe happy and get all cuddled up with him hehe
	Mabel: Thought: Even though it's a little crazy
do advance_time(4, 0)
Mabel: Uhm babe? You gonna be here soon?
Player: Yeah on the way
Mabel: Oh great..
Mabel: Quick question. Does this outfit look good?
Mabel: img: mabel/164
Mabel: Let me know if its a bit too much 😅
- It's not too much
	Player: It's not too much
	Player: I like it
	Mabel: Phew
- Damn Mabes!
	Player: Damn Mabes!
	Mabel: Omg too, much too much isn't it
	Player: Not at all
	Player: It's great
Mabel: I don't know what to expect
Player: What happened to being the party princess
Mabel: Oh would you look at the time!
Mabel: Gotta go 😇
Player: 😆
do advance_time(0, 17)
do Story.set_location(\"college_square_gardens\")
Player: Just got here
Mabel: Great! I'm omw
Mabel: Almost there
Mabel: img: mabel/165
Mabel: I feel like I stand out too much
Mabel: Or that Because I stand out, I fit in...
Mabel: Does that make any sense?
Player: Not one bit
Mabel: 😒
Player: 😇
Mabel: Thought: Gee it feels like everyone I pass looks at me
Mabel: Thought: I should walk a little faster
Player: Can't wait to see you
Mabel: Me neither 🥰
do advance_time(1, 0)
do Story.set_location(\"photography_club_house\")
Player: Where did you go?
Mabel: Bathroom nervousness lol
Player: You're gonna miss all the snacks
